NAME
    Plack::Middleware::Hoptoad - Sends application errors to Hoptoad

SYNOPSIS
      enable "Hoptoad", api_key => "...";

DESCRIPTION
    This middleware catches exceptions (run-time errors) happening in your
    application and sends them to <Hoptoad>.

AUTHOR
    Tatsuhiko Miyagawa

